items.title: Dillard's Q1 Earnings Preview: What Mixed Trends Mean for Investors?
items.description: DDS's Q1 results are expected to reflect the benefits of growth opportunities in brick-and-mortar and e-commerce businesses amid a tough retail environment and cautious buying behavior.
